text: The Barahona amphisbaena (Amphisbaena hyporissor) is a species of worm lizards found in Hispaniola. ==References== hyporissor Category:Reptiles described in 1965 Category:Taxa named by Richard Thomas (herpetologist) Category:Endemic fauna of Hispaniola Category:Reptiles of the Dominican Republic Category:Reptiles of Haiti
title: Barahona amphisbaena
